" es de los primeros que aprenden los jóvenes magos ghitu._#','#_용도가 다양한 "불의 건틀렛"은 젊은 기투 마법사들이 초반에 배우는 주문들 중 하나이다._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('445958','Firesong and Sunspeaker','DOM','Legendary Creature — Minotaur Cleric','R','{4}{R}{W}','6','4','6',NULL,'Red instant and sorcery spells you control have lifelink.£Whenever a white instant or sorcery spell causes you to gain life, Firesong and Sunspeaker deals 3 damage to target creature or player.','#_The peaks of Hurloon never fall silent._#',NULL,'Zoltan Boros','280','5','£4/27/2018: If a source you control with lifelink deals damage to you, you gain and lose that much life simultaneously. Your life total doesn’t change.£4/27/2018: The last ability of Firesong and Sunspeaker can’t target a planeswalker.£4/27/2018: A spell causes you to gain life if its cost or effect instructs you to gain life or if an instruction in its cost or effect is modified by a replacement effect and the modified event includes you gaining life. If a spell’s cost or effect instructs a source with lifelink you control to deal damage, that spell causes that life gain as well.£4/27/2018: If a white instant or sorcery spell you don’t control causes you to gain life, Firesong and Sunspeaker’s last ability triggers.£4/27/2018: If you gain an amount of life “for each” of something, that life is gained as one event and Firesong and Sunspeaker’s last ability triggers only once.£4/27/2018: Firesong and Sunspeaker’s last ability doesn’t trigger if a triggered ability of a white instant or sorcery spell or card causes you to gain life, such as the triggered ability of Renewed Faith when it’s cycled.£4/27/2018: If a red and white spell you control deals damage to multiple things using the word “deals” only once, Firesong and Sunspeaker’s last ability triggers only once. Similarly, if a red and white spell’s effect causes it to deal damage to one thing and then deal more damage with a second instance of the word “dea