estrictions of the cards you cast from exile.£4/27/2018: You’ll still pay all costs for that spell, including additional costs. You may also pay alternative costs such as that granted by Jodah, Archmage Eternal.£4/27/2018: The exiled cards aren’t in your hand, so you can’t cycle them, discard them, or activate any of their activated abilities.£4/27/2018: Once you begin to cast a card, losing control of Rona won’t affect the spell.£4/27/2018: The card you’ll exile from the top of your library is determined as Rona’s last ability resolves. This might not be the card that was on top of your library when you activated that ability.£4/27/2018: A card, spell, or permanent is historic if it has the legendary supertype, the artifact card type, or the Saga subtype. Having two of those qualities doesn’t make an object more historic than another or provide an additional bonus—an object either is historic or it isn’t.','UB (O)',NULL,'0.01','0.2','2.77',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'UB','基克斯信徒罗娜','基克斯信徒羅娜','Rona, disciple de Gix','Rona, Schülerin des Gix','Rona, Discepola di Gix','ギックスの信奉者、ローナ','Rona, Discípula de Gix','Рона, Ученица Гикса','Rona, discípula de Gix','긱스의 제자, 로나','传奇生物 ～人类／神器师','傳奇生物 ～人類／神器師','Créature légendaire : humain et artificier','Legendäre Kreatur — Mensch, Handwerker','Creatura Leggendaria — Artefice Umano','伝説のクリーチャー ― 人間・工匠','Criatura Lendária — Humano Artesão','Легендарное Существо — Человек Механик','Criatura legendaria — Artífice humano','전설적 생물 — 인간 기능공','当基克斯信徒罗娜进战场时，你可以将目标史迹牌从你的坟墓场放逐。（神器、传奇和传纪是史迹。）£你可以施放以罗娜放逐的非地牌。£{4}，{T}：放逐你的牌库顶牌。','當基克斯信徒羅娜進戰場時，你可以將目標史跡牌從你的墳墓場放逐。（神器、傳奇和傳紀是史跡。）£你可以施放以羅娜放逐的非地牌。£{4}，{T}：放逐你的牌庫頂牌。','Quand Rona, disciple de Gix arrive sur le champ de bataille, vous pouvez exiler une carte historique ciblée depuis votre cimetière. #_(Les artefacts, les légendaires et les sagas sont historiques.)_#£Vous pouvez lancer des cartes non-terrain exilées par Rona.£{4}, {T} : Exilez la carte du dessus de votre bibliothèque.','Wenn Rona, Schülerin des G